 <div class="cmt"> <p>I agree with Randy. I believe the website user is more educated on the general layout of a site. It seems most corporate websites today abide by the same design principles which in turn create a familiar environment for the user.  I think also that reliable, drill-down menu systems offer greater access to content without having to search.</p></div>

  
  
